# Interactive Logo

- Visual style: 
  - Stacked format with "[V]iet", middle word, and "[H]ack" vertically aligned
  - First characters of each word are in square brackets
  - Consistent spacing between first character and rest of word
- Behavior:
  - Rotates through various middle words (Roc, Travel, DMPN, etc.)
  - Shows rare variants occasionally or when triggered
- Animation:
  - Smooth transition between variants
  - Special visual effects for rare variants
- Implementation: 
  - Responsive text sizing across devices
  - Proper vertical alignment of first characters 